                    "value": "\n            <p>kind loan of a melodeon, and to all others<lb/> who, though, their names may not\n                be<lb/> mentioned here, have assisted in the cere-<lb/>monies.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Resolved. That a copy of these<lb/> resolutions be sent to each of\n                the reverend<lb/> gentlemen and others herein mentioned,<lb/> and that they be\n                inserted for publication<lb/> in the Ledger, Daily Register, Freie<lb/> Heimath and\n                Democrat.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\"><persName role=\"author\">Weidnitzer</persName>, Secr.</p>\n            <div>\n                <p>\n                    <ref target=\"Occident_PDFs/Occ_12_2.pdf\">The above text refers to Occident\n                        Volume 12 No. 2 pages 114 through 115. Click here to view.</ref>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n"
